				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't know if the final reveal actually works. There's such a good buildup of dread &#8212; I was reminded of the one about the antenna broadcasting the little girl counting down in Russian. But actually seeing the source of the tension was possibly going to be a letdown regardless of what it was.</p> <p>Still, upvoting because this is definitely a good article. Those containment procedures are a good hook, and this coming from someone who usually ignores them on Safe and Euclid articles. :)</p> 
				 	]]>
